             | zabbix server |          (Server and Agent can be the same host)
             |        :10051 |
  .----------------.         |
  | T  .------------.        |
  | E  | H  .-------.        |
  | M  | O  | ITEMS |        |                   .---------------------------.
  | P  | S  | ITEMS |        |------------------>| request:{name,ip,item}    |
  | L  | T  | ITEMS |        |                   '---------------------------'
  | A  |    | ITEMS |        |                         *not dns name :(
  | T  |    | ITEMS |        |                                 |
  | E  |    | ITEMS |        |                                 |
  '----'----'-------'        |                                 v
             '---------------'                      .--------------------.
                     ^                              | AWS security group |
                     |                              '--------------------'
          .--------------------.                               |
          | AWS security group |                               v
          '--------------------'               .------------------------------.
                     ^                         | zabbix agent                 |
                     |                         | :10050                       |
       .--------------------------.            |                              |
       | return: {name,key,value} |<-----------| name: agentd.conf's hostname |
       '--------------------------'            |                              |
             *not dns name :(         .---------------------------------------.
