               |                      | UserParameter=cloudwatch.dimension[*] |
               |                      '---------------------------------------'
               |                                          |
               |                                          v
               |                      .---------------------------------------.
               |                      | /usr/local/bin/zabbix-cloudwatch.py   |
 .----------------------------.       |                                       |
 | chef                       |       | accounts: aws_key,aws_secret          |
 | .--------------------------.       '---------------------------------------'
 | | role: myrole.rb          |
 | |   - accounts information |
